[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:00:13.122 --> 00:00:19.085 align:middle line:84%
>> I'm Dr. Theresa Bullard, and
this is "Mystery Teachings."

00:00:19.085 --> 00:00:23.450 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:00:23.450 --> 00:00:26.600 align:middle line:84%
Can we make sense of
our physical experience

00:00:26.600 --> 00:00:30.260 align:middle line:84%
and become players in
the symphony of life?

00:00:30.260 --> 00:00:33.680 align:middle line:84%
Can we gain insights into
the fundamental formulas

00:00:33.680 --> 00:00:37.580 align:middle line:84%
of creation and grasp
the mind of God?

00:00:37.580 --> 00:00:40.400 align:middle line:10%
There are many challenges
we must face, however,

00:00:40.400 --> 00:00:44.000 align:middle line:10%
in our quest to discovering
such a worthy prize.

00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:47.780 align:middle line:10%
In this episode, we discover
what those challenges are,

00:00:47.780 --> 00:00:50.540 align:middle line:10%
the progress that has been
made in overcoming them,

00:00:50.540 --> 00:00:53.795 align:middle line:10%
and why this search for unity
is so important to our lives.

00:00:53.795 --> 00:00:56.580 align:middle line:90%


00:00:56.580 --> 00:00:59.410 align:middle line:84%
The two main pillars
of modern physics

00:00:59.410 --> 00:01:01.780 align:middle line:84%
are quantum field
theory, which deals

00:01:01.780 --> 00:01:06.130 align:middle line:84%
with microcosmic behaviors, and
general relativity, which deals

00:01:06.130 --> 00:01:08.410 align:middle line:90%
with macrocosmic behaviors.

00:01:08.410 --> 00:01:10.750 align:middle line:84%
We've all heard the
four physical forces

00:01:10.750 --> 00:01:13.870 align:middle line:84%
of gravity, electromagnetism,
and the weak and strong

00:01:13.870 --> 00:01:15.400 align:middle line:90%
nuclear forces.

00:01:15.400 --> 00:01:17.530 align:middle line:84%
Quantum mechanics
has successfully

00:01:17.530 --> 00:01:21.290 align:middle line:84%
been able to unify three
of the four forces.

00:01:21.290 --> 00:01:23.770 align:middle line:90%
But it does not explain gravity.

00:01:23.770 --> 00:01:25.450 align:middle line:84%
General relativity,
on the other hand,

00:01:25.450 --> 00:01:29.020 align:middle line:84%
explains gravity, but from
a classical physics approach

00:01:29.020 --> 00:01:32.200 align:middle line:84%
that doesn't incorporate
quantum phenomenon.

00:01:32.200 --> 00:01:34.030 align:middle line:84%
The challenge
physicists encounter

00:01:34.030 --> 00:01:37.660 align:middle line:84%
is that these two approaches
become incompatible

00:01:37.660 --> 00:01:41.650 align:middle line:84%
when dealing with very
small scales yet high mass,

00:01:41.650 --> 00:01:44.140 align:middle line:84%
such as would be
found in a black hole

00:01:44.140 --> 00:01:48.130 align:middle line:84%
or at the singularity in the
first moment of the Big Bang.

00:01:48.130 --> 00:01:51.760 align:middle line:84%
Attempts to incorporate
gravity into the standard model

00:01:51.760 --> 00:01:54.880 align:middle line:84%
of quantum physics run
up against infinities

00:01:54.880 --> 00:01:56.770 align:middle line:90%
and deep paradoxes.

00:01:56.770 --> 00:01:58.960 align:middle line:84%
This has forced
physicists to come up

00:01:58.960 --> 00:02:01.930 align:middle line:90%
with entirely new models.

00:02:01.930 --> 00:02:04.240 align:middle line:84%
Why should we care what
happens in black holes

00:02:04.240 --> 00:02:05.920 align:middle line:90%
or big-bang singularities?

00:02:05.920 --> 00:02:10.100 align:middle line:84%
How does this knowledge have
any relevance to our lives?

00:02:10.100 --> 00:02:13.090 align:middle line:10%
Well, the reason is that
this search for unity

00:02:13.090 --> 00:02:18.010 align:middle line:10%
is also the search for us to
know ourselves and our origin.

00:02:18.010 --> 00:02:21.130 align:middle line:90%
Where do we come from?

00:02:21.130 --> 00:02:24.010 align:middle line:84%
The more we can understand
our origins the more

00:02:24.010 --> 00:02:26.500 align:middle line:90%
we can understand our true self.

00:02:26.500 --> 00:02:28.960 align:middle line:84%
Only then will we
know what it takes

00:02:28.960 --> 00:02:32.390 align:middle line:90%
to tap into our full potential.

00:02:32.390 --> 00:02:33.790 align:middle line:84%
The fact that
physicists have now

00:02:33.790 --> 00:02:37.510 align:middle line:84%
started moving beyond
ordinary notions of spacetime

00:02:37.510 --> 00:02:39.580 align:middle line:84%
and material ways
of thinking in order

00:02:39.580 --> 00:02:42.040 align:middle line:84%
to find their
theory of everything

00:02:42.040 --> 00:02:45.940 align:middle line:84%
reveals that there is a deeper
underlying reality where

00:02:45.940 --> 00:02:48.820 align:middle line:84%
everything is an
unbroken wholeness.

00:02:48.820 --> 00:02:53.650 align:middle line:84%
A unity that is the source of
all phenomenon in our universe.

00:02:53.650 --> 00:02:58.060 align:middle line:84%
And to grasp this unity we need
to go through a paradigm shift

00:02:58.060 --> 00:03:00.190 align:middle line:84%
in our ways of thinking
and approaching issues.

00:03:00.190 --> 00:03:04.110 align:middle line:90%


00:03:04.110 --> 00:03:07.050 align:middle line:84%
What kinds of paradigm
shifts are happening now?

00:03:07.050 --> 00:03:09.750 align:middle line:84%
There are a couple of
themes revealing themselves

00:03:09.750 --> 00:03:11.730 align:middle line:84%
as we consider the
current leading

00:03:11.730 --> 00:03:14.370 align:middle line:84%
models that attempt
to unite quantum

00:03:14.370 --> 00:03:16.770 align:middle line:90%
physics and general relativity.

00:03:16.770 --> 00:03:20.550 align:middle line:84%
One of those recurring themes
is that spacetime, matter,

00:03:20.550 --> 00:03:24.330 align:middle line:84%
and even energy are no
longer seen as fundamental,

00:03:24.330 --> 00:03:26.730 align:middle line:84%
but, rather, as
emergent properties out

00:03:26.730 --> 00:03:28.660 align:middle line:90%
of some deeper reality.

00:03:28.660 --> 00:03:30.630 align:middle line:90%
What is meant by emergent?

00:03:30.630 --> 00:03:33.930 align:middle line:84%
The best way to describe
it is to think of water.

00:03:33.930 --> 00:03:36.510 align:middle line:90%
Water is made of H2O molecules.

00:03:36.510 --> 00:03:38.790 align:middle line:84%
Those molecules in
and of themselves

00:03:38.790 --> 00:03:41.610 align:middle line:84%
do not have the
quality of being wet.

00:03:41.610 --> 00:03:44.430 align:middle line:84%
They can be in the air
state as they evaporate,

00:03:44.430 --> 00:03:47.610 align:middle line:84%
they can also be in a frozen
and crystallized state,

00:03:47.610 --> 00:03:49.650 align:middle line:90%
or they can even feel dry.

00:03:49.650 --> 00:03:53.370 align:middle line:84%
The H2O molecules are
discrete and individualized,

00:03:53.370 --> 00:03:56.550 align:middle line:84%
yet the water appears to
be continuous, flowing,

00:03:56.550 --> 00:03:58.140 align:middle line:90%
and transparent.

00:03:58.140 --> 00:04:00.330 align:middle line:84%
All of these
properties of water are

00:04:00.330 --> 00:04:05.010 align:middle line:84%
emergent as a result of how
the H2O molecules interact

00:04:05.010 --> 00:04:08.340 align:middle line:84%
with one another at
different temperatures.

00:04:08.340 --> 00:04:12.660 align:middle line:84%
We often picture space and time
as the fundamental backdrops

00:04:12.660 --> 00:04:15.810 align:middle line:84%
to the universe, while matter
and energy are its building

00:04:15.810 --> 00:04:16.610 align:middle line:90%
blocks.

00:04:16.610 --> 00:04:19.779 align:middle line:84%
But these new models are saying
that that is not the case.

00:04:19.779 --> 00:04:21.750 align:middle line:84%
Instead, they are
just properties

00:04:21.750 --> 00:04:25.710 align:middle line:84%
that emerge as a result of
interactions taking place

00:04:25.710 --> 00:04:30.210 align:middle line:84%
within a deeper reality, just
as water's properties emerge

00:04:30.210 --> 00:04:32.790 align:middle line:84%
from the water molecules
and their interactions

00:04:32.790 --> 00:04:34.680 align:middle line:90%
with each other.

00:04:34.680 --> 00:04:36.510 align:middle line:90%
What is this deeper reality?

00:04:36.510 --> 00:04:38.190 align:middle line:90%
That is the question.

00:04:38.190 --> 00:04:40.950 align:middle line:84%
To grasp it, we have
to completely change

00:04:40.950 --> 00:04:43.770 align:middle line:90%
our notions of what is real.

00:04:43.770 --> 00:04:46.540 align:middle line:84%
Space, time, energy,
and matter are only

00:04:46.540 --> 00:04:50.790 align:middle line:84%
experiential attributes of
the deeper underlying reality,

00:04:50.790 --> 00:04:54.250 align:middle line:84%
similar to how water,
ice, or moist air

00:04:54.250 --> 00:04:58.140 align:middle line:84%
are experiential attributes
of H2O molecules interacting.

00:04:58.140 --> 00:05:00.450 align:middle line:84%
We can experience these
different emergent

00:05:00.450 --> 00:05:03.300 align:middle line:84%
states of water, but
we can't directly

00:05:03.300 --> 00:05:07.980 align:middle line:84%
experience a single H2O molecule
with our five physical senses.

00:05:07.980 --> 00:05:10.770 align:middle line:84%
We can, however, experience
it with our mind.

00:05:10.770 --> 00:05:13.930 align:middle line:90%


00:05:13.930 --> 00:05:16.000 align:middle line:84%
Due to the knowledge
gained from science

00:05:16.000 --> 00:05:18.670 align:middle line:84%
with its observational
tools, we are now

00:05:18.670 --> 00:05:21.970 align:middle line:84%
more informed about how
to visualize and imagine

00:05:21.970 --> 00:05:24.810 align:middle line:90%
a single molecule of water.

00:05:24.810 --> 00:05:26.460 align:middle line:84%
Equipped with this
knowledge, we can

00:05:26.460 --> 00:05:28.650 align:middle line:84%
use our consciousness
to interact

00:05:28.650 --> 00:05:30.610 align:middle line:90%
with its consciousness.

00:05:30.610 --> 00:05:33.810 align:middle line:84%
We have proof of this from
the work of Dr. Masaru Emoto,

00:05:33.810 --> 00:05:36.400 align:middle line:84%
who demonstrated the
impact of our thoughts,

00:05:36.400 --> 00:05:38.940 align:middle line:84%
emotions, and vibrational
state of being

00:05:38.940 --> 00:05:42.150 align:middle line:90%
and what they have upon water.

00:05:42.150 --> 00:05:45.180 align:middle line:84%
At the same time, long
before science told us

00:05:45.180 --> 00:05:48.630 align:middle line:84%
about H2O molecules,
ancient shamans, alchemists,

00:05:48.630 --> 00:05:52.890 align:middle line:84%
and mystics did have ways of
communicating and interacting

00:05:52.890 --> 00:05:55.200 align:middle line:90%
with invisible essences.

00:05:55.200 --> 00:05:58.200 align:middle line:84%
They thought of them as spirit
beings, such as elementals,

00:05:58.200 --> 00:06:00.720 align:middle line:84%
divas, and angels,
as the consciousness

00:06:00.720 --> 00:06:03.120 align:middle line:90%
behind all materia.

00:06:03.120 --> 00:06:06.210 align:middle line:84%
They might not have known
the specific shape of an H2O

00:06:06.210 --> 00:06:09.150 align:middle line:84%
molecule, for example,
but they certainly

00:06:09.150 --> 00:06:12.840 align:middle line:84%
mastered the art of conscious
communication with the elements

00:06:12.840 --> 00:06:15.360 align:middle line:90%
and how to harness their power.

00:06:15.360 --> 00:06:18.210 align:middle line:84%
As science comes closer to
understanding the deeper

00:06:18.210 --> 00:06:20.730 align:middle line:84%
reality, it can
similarly help us

00:06:20.730 --> 00:06:24.300 align:middle line:84%
to connect with it through
our mind and consciousness.

00:06:24.300 --> 00:06:27.510 align:middle line:84%
If we can use our consciousness
to properly communicate

00:06:27.510 --> 00:06:29.820 align:middle line:84%
with the deeper
reality, then we can

00:06:29.820 --> 00:06:33.150 align:middle line:84%
begin to impact how
it manifests itself

00:06:33.150 --> 00:06:35.640 align:middle line:90%
into our experiential realm.

00:06:35.640 --> 00:06:38.430 align:middle line:10%
Just like we're able
to influence the shapes

00:06:38.430 --> 00:06:42.780 align:middle line:10%
and beauty of water crystals
with our vibrational essence,

00:06:42.780 --> 00:06:46.560 align:middle line:10%
science is one part of
it, art is the other.

00:06:46.560 --> 00:06:49.290 align:middle line:84%
Science informs
us, and art is how

00:06:49.290 --> 00:06:53.070 align:middle line:84%
we use that and express
or directly interact

00:06:53.070 --> 00:06:54.540 align:middle line:90%
with consciousness.

00:06:54.540 --> 00:06:56.700 align:middle line:84%
Metaphysics is about
bringing together

00:06:56.700 --> 00:06:59.130 align:middle line:84%
both the art and
the science in order

00:06:59.130 --> 00:07:02.010 align:middle line:84%
to achieve true
mastery and awakening

00:07:02.010 --> 00:07:03.555 align:middle line:90%
of our full potential.

00:07:03.555 --> 00:07:06.720 align:middle line:84%
Now let's go back to the
other themes that show up

00:07:06.720 --> 00:07:08.370 align:middle line:90%
in the newer physics models.

00:07:08.370 --> 00:07:09.990 align:middle line:90%
What more is there?

00:07:09.990 --> 00:07:13.920 align:middle line:84%
Concepts such as
supersymmetry, superfluidity,

00:07:13.920 --> 00:07:18.420 align:middle line:84%
higher dimensions, holographic
information, coherence,

00:07:18.420 --> 00:07:21.570 align:middle line:84%
and a geometric
nature to the universe

00:07:21.570 --> 00:07:23.640 align:middle line:90%
are all being proposed.

00:07:23.640 --> 00:07:25.740 align:middle line:84%
What do all of
these things mean?

00:07:25.740 --> 00:07:29.310 align:middle line:84%
To explore that let's dive into
a few of the leading physics

00:07:29.310 --> 00:07:31.770 align:middle line:90%
models for unifying physics.

00:07:31.770 --> 00:07:33.990 align:middle line:84%
The first and most
popular models

00:07:33.990 --> 00:07:37.080 align:middle line:84%
are various string theories and
something called loop quantum

00:07:37.080 --> 00:07:38.040 align:middle line:90%
gravity.

00:07:38.040 --> 00:07:39.870 align:middle line:84%
We explore these
in other episodes,

00:07:39.870 --> 00:07:43.470 align:middle line:84%
but string theory
especially is very elegant

00:07:43.470 --> 00:07:46.350 align:middle line:84%
and it lends itself
well to correlations

00:07:46.350 --> 00:07:49.170 align:middle line:84%
with hermetic, alchemical,
and other ancient spiritual

00:07:49.170 --> 00:07:50.370 align:middle line:90%
principles.

00:07:50.370 --> 00:07:54.600 align:middle line:84%
In essence, these models say
that the fundamental components

00:07:54.600 --> 00:07:57.360 align:middle line:84%
of that deeper reality
are harmonically

00:07:57.360 --> 00:08:03.330 align:middle line:84%
vibrating strings, membranes,
or loops of braided spacetime.

00:08:03.330 --> 00:08:05.490 align:middle line:84%
But this deeper
reality can only be

00:08:05.490 --> 00:08:08.760 align:middle line:84%
found at the smallest
microcosmic scale called

00:08:08.760 --> 00:08:12.030 align:middle line:84%
the Planck scale,
which is very tiny.

00:08:12.030 --> 00:08:14.640 align:middle line:84%
This scale is far
too small for even

00:08:14.640 --> 00:08:17.580 align:middle line:84%
our most powerful detectors
and particle accelerators

00:08:17.580 --> 00:08:19.600 align:middle line:90%
to access directly.

00:08:19.600 --> 00:08:22.170 align:middle line:84%
But string theory does
make several predictions

00:08:22.170 --> 00:08:25.950 align:middle line:84%
beyond what the standard
model has already verified.

00:08:25.950 --> 00:08:28.440 align:middle line:84%
The main new predictions
include a host

00:08:28.440 --> 00:08:31.080 align:middle line:84%
of new supersymmetric
particles, which

00:08:31.080 --> 00:08:33.330 align:middle line:84%
could account for much
of the dark matter that

00:08:33.330 --> 00:08:35.130 align:middle line:90%
fills the galaxies.

00:08:35.130 --> 00:08:38.400 align:middle line:84%
They also predict that there
are 10 spatial dimensions

00:08:38.400 --> 00:08:41.190 align:middle line:84%
plus time, causing
us to consider

00:08:41.190 --> 00:08:43.380 align:middle line:90%
our multi-dimensionality.

00:08:43.380 --> 00:08:46.500 align:middle line:84%
And it tells us that the
laws of string theory

00:08:46.500 --> 00:08:49.380 align:middle line:84%
are equivalent to the
laws of harmony, which

00:08:49.380 --> 00:08:51.780 align:middle line:84%
relate to music,
sacred geometry,

00:08:51.780 --> 00:08:54.394 align:middle line:84%
and what creates
beauty in our world.

00:08:54.394 --> 00:08:56.310 align:middle line:84%
These are some of the
things that I personally

00:08:56.310 --> 00:08:58.800 align:middle line:84%
love about string theory
and do hope that they

00:08:58.800 --> 00:09:01.530 align:middle line:90%
will be verified one day.

00:09:01.530 --> 00:09:04.500 align:middle line:84%
String theory also plays a
role in the holographic model

00:09:04.500 --> 00:09:06.480 align:middle line:90%
explored in other episodes.

00:09:06.480 --> 00:09:09.120 align:middle line:84%
It says the vibrations
of these strings

00:09:09.120 --> 00:09:12.630 align:middle line:84%
create waves or ripples
in the quantum sea.

00:09:12.630 --> 00:09:16.230 align:middle line:84%
As those waves combine, they
create interference patterns

00:09:16.230 --> 00:09:18.700 align:middle line:90%
that contain information.

00:09:18.700 --> 00:09:22.980 align:middle line:84%
This information is encoded
upon the surface of the quantum

00:09:22.980 --> 00:09:26.370 align:middle line:84%
vacuum within the
zero point field.

00:09:26.370 --> 00:09:28.170 align:middle line:84%
It's the information
patterns that

00:09:28.170 --> 00:09:30.960 align:middle line:84%
govern the formation
of our universe

00:09:30.960 --> 00:09:33.480 align:middle line:84%
as well as the types
of particles and forces

00:09:33.480 --> 00:09:35.670 align:middle line:90%
that can be manifested.

00:09:35.670 --> 00:09:38.010 align:middle line:84%
Some scientists have
delved even deeper

00:09:38.010 --> 00:09:40.380 align:middle line:84%
into this analogy of
the quantum vacuum

00:09:40.380 --> 00:09:43.050 align:middle line:90%
as being like a vast ocean.

00:09:43.050 --> 00:09:45.810 align:middle line:84%
If particles are more
like waves traveling

00:09:45.810 --> 00:09:48.900 align:middle line:84%
upon the surface of the
sea, and if spacetime

00:09:48.900 --> 00:09:51.750 align:middle line:84%
is analogous to a
liquid, then physicists

00:09:51.750 --> 00:09:55.710 align:middle line:84%
say it must be more like a
superfluid, one that does not

00:09:55.710 --> 00:09:59.250 align:middle line:84%
impose any kind of friction,
limitation, or dampening

00:09:59.250 --> 00:10:00.995 align:middle line:90%
of the movement of those waves.

00:10:00.995 --> 00:10:02.590 align:middle line:90%
Now what does that mean?

00:10:02.590 --> 00:10:05.070 align:middle line:84%
Well, it means that the
essence of the quantum vacuum

00:10:05.070 --> 00:10:07.560 align:middle line:84%
is not physical, at
least in the ways

00:10:07.560 --> 00:10:09.660 align:middle line:84%
that we're usually
thinking of it.

00:10:09.660 --> 00:10:13.800 align:middle line:84%
Or we might also say that
spacetime does not actually

00:10:13.800 --> 00:10:18.390 align:middle line:84%
impose any limitations when
we connect with that deeper

00:10:18.390 --> 00:10:20.620 align:middle line:90%
reality.

00:10:20.620 --> 00:10:23.430 align:middle line:84%
The final scientific
approach to unifying physics

00:10:23.430 --> 00:10:27.560 align:middle line:84%
that is really worth exploring
is one that is relatively new.

00:10:27.560 --> 00:10:30.350 align:middle line:10%
In 2013, physicists
from the Institute

00:10:30.350 --> 00:10:32.240 align:middle line:10%
of Advanced Studies
in New Jersey

00:10:32.240 --> 00:10:35.690 align:middle line:10%
published their findings of
a new mathematical object

00:10:35.690 --> 00:10:38.820 align:middle line:10%
they call the amplituhedron.

00:10:38.820 --> 00:10:41.550 align:middle line:10%
In essence, it is a
multi-dimensional series

00:10:41.550 --> 00:10:44.310 align:middle line:10%
of interconnected
polyhedra, and it

00:10:44.310 --> 00:10:48.330 align:middle line:10%
looks like an intricate jewel
of higher dimensionality.

00:10:48.330 --> 00:10:51.450 align:middle line:84%
The simplest version of it
consists of four tetrahedra

00:10:51.450 --> 00:10:53.610 align:middle line:90%
connected by their faces.

00:10:53.610 --> 00:10:57.630 align:middle line:84%
This shape does not actually
exist in physical space.

00:10:57.630 --> 00:11:02.340 align:middle line:84%
Rather, it is a purely abstract
object that exists only

00:11:02.340 --> 00:11:04.420 align:middle line:90%
in a mathematical space.

00:11:04.420 --> 00:11:07.770 align:middle line:84%
It allows scientists to
model particle interactions

00:11:07.770 --> 00:11:09.490 align:middle line:90%
in a much simpler way.

00:11:09.490 --> 00:11:13.080 align:middle line:84%
And there is not just one
amplituhedron, but many,

00:11:13.080 --> 00:11:15.570 align:middle line:84%
each depending on
the various particles

00:11:15.570 --> 00:11:18.180 align:middle line:84%
interacting and all
the different ways

00:11:18.180 --> 00:11:19.740 align:middle line:90%
that they can interact.

00:11:19.740 --> 00:11:23.010 align:middle line:84%
These dictate the
dimensionality and facets

00:11:23.010 --> 00:11:26.190 align:middle line:90%
of that geometrical jewel.

00:11:26.190 --> 00:11:29.160 align:middle line:84%
What used to take thousands
of equations and Feynman

00:11:29.160 --> 00:11:34.050 align:middle line:84%
diagrams can now be done in a
simple one-line formula that

00:11:34.050 --> 00:11:38.640 align:middle line:84%
just calculates the volume
of the underlying geometry.

00:11:38.640 --> 00:11:40.360 align:middle line:90%
So what does this mean?

00:11:40.360 --> 00:11:44.350 align:middle line:84%
Well, it points to a geometrical
basis to the universe.

00:11:44.350 --> 00:11:46.950 align:middle line:84%
This is what I personally
love about this approach.

00:11:46.950 --> 00:11:49.800 align:middle line:84%
In addition to its
paradigm-shifting perspective,

00:11:49.800 --> 00:11:53.190 align:middle line:84%
it says that geometry
underlies everything.

00:11:53.190 --> 00:11:55.800 align:middle line:84%
Now this idea is not
new to those of us who

00:11:55.800 --> 00:11:58.530 align:middle line:84%
study sacred geometry,
which dates back

00:11:58.530 --> 00:12:00.870 align:middle line:84%
far beyond the
Pythagorean mystery school

00:12:00.870 --> 00:12:03.100 align:middle line:90%
and to ancient Egypt and beyond.

00:12:03.100 --> 00:12:06.630 align:middle line:84%
But what is great about this
is that science is again

00:12:06.630 --> 00:12:09.570 align:middle line:84%
catching up with what ancient
metaphysical teachings have

00:12:09.570 --> 00:12:12.030 align:middle line:90%
been saying for millennia.

00:12:12.030 --> 00:12:15.450 align:middle line:84%
Sacred geometry governs
the true building blocks

00:12:15.450 --> 00:12:17.850 align:middle line:90%
and fabric of our universe.

00:12:17.850 --> 00:12:22.980 align:middle line:84%
This model is peering into
an entirely different world,

00:12:22.980 --> 00:12:26.250 align:middle line:84%
one of pure number and
geometry rather than

00:12:26.250 --> 00:12:30.030 align:middle line:84%
one based in spacetime
and quantum probabilities.

00:12:30.030 --> 00:12:32.640 align:middle line:84%
It threw those
assumptions out the window

00:12:32.640 --> 00:12:36.120 align:middle line:84%
and stepped into an
entirely different mindset.

00:12:36.120 --> 00:12:38.760 align:middle line:84%
One of the reasons that
most attempts to find

00:12:38.760 --> 00:12:41.100 align:middle line:84%
a quantum gravity
have failed thus far

00:12:41.100 --> 00:12:44.640 align:middle line:84%
is that they run into this
issue with two core assumptions

00:12:44.640 --> 00:12:47.200 align:middle line:84%
that physicists make
about our universe.

00:12:47.200 --> 00:12:51.090 align:middle line:84%
These are known as unitarity
and locality, and both of them

00:12:51.090 --> 00:12:55.110 align:middle line:84%
are based on old
materialistic paradigms.

00:12:55.110 --> 00:12:59.370 align:middle line:84%
Unitarity means that all quantum
probabilities for a given

00:12:59.370 --> 00:13:02.670 align:middle line:84%
set of particle
interactions must add to 1,

00:13:02.670 --> 00:13:04.680 align:middle line:84%
similar to how we
add percentages

00:13:04.680 --> 00:13:06.930 align:middle line:90%
until we get to 100%.

00:13:06.930 --> 00:13:10.200 align:middle line:84%
But this assumption
breaks down when gravity

00:13:10.200 --> 00:13:12.630 align:middle line:90%
gets involved at small scales.

00:13:12.630 --> 00:13:14.520 align:middle line:10%
Locality, on the
other hand, assumes

00:13:14.520 --> 00:13:19.150 align:middle line:10%
that particles can only interact
through proximity in spacetime.

00:13:19.150 --> 00:13:22.650 align:middle line:10%
But we know from entanglement
that this is not entirely true,

00:13:22.650 --> 00:13:26.700 align:middle line:10%
and, again, it breaks down for
quantum gravity situations.

00:13:26.700 --> 00:13:29.370 align:middle line:84%
The failure of these
assumptions suggests

00:13:29.370 --> 00:13:32.820 align:middle line:84%
that physics needs to be
reformulated without either

00:13:32.820 --> 00:13:34.470 align:middle line:90%
of those old principles.

00:13:34.470 --> 00:13:38.550 align:middle line:84%
And this is exactly what the
amplituhedron approach does.

00:13:38.550 --> 00:13:40.590 align:middle line:84%
By doing so, it
suggests that there

00:13:40.590 --> 00:13:44.790 align:middle line:84%
is a coherent geometrical
structure at the foundation

00:13:44.790 --> 00:13:49.530 align:middle line:84%
of the universe, while spacetime
locality and unitary of quantum

00:13:49.530 --> 00:13:52.860 align:middle line:84%
probabilities are emergent
phenomenon that are

00:13:52.860 --> 00:13:55.710 align:middle line:90%
a consequence of the geometry.

00:13:55.710 --> 00:13:58.950 align:middle line:84%
In other words, the
existence of spacetime

00:13:58.950 --> 00:14:01.560 align:middle line:84%
and the particle interactions
that take place within it

00:14:01.560 --> 00:14:04.320 align:middle line:90%
are a result of geometry.

00:14:04.320 --> 00:14:05.840 align:middle line:90%
Geometry of what?

00:14:05.840 --> 00:14:08.080 align:middle line:90%
What is it made of?

00:14:08.080 --> 00:14:09.510 align:middle line:84%
Well, the basic
idea is that it's

00:14:09.510 --> 00:14:11.970 align:middle line:84%
made of something
like rays of light

00:14:11.970 --> 00:14:16.505 align:middle line:84%
called twisters that exist in
a purely mathematical space.

00:14:16.505 --> 00:14:20.520 align:middle line:84%
And what this reminds me of are
the rays of creation discussed

00:14:20.520 --> 00:14:23.250 align:middle line:84%
in other episodes that
come from the Ein Sof,

00:14:23.250 --> 00:14:26.880 align:middle line:84%
the infinite source prior
to our physical universe

00:14:26.880 --> 00:14:31.110 align:middle line:84%
coming into being, meaning
they originate somewhere beyond

00:14:31.110 --> 00:14:35.460 align:middle line:84%
or transcendent to our
physical spacetime universe.

00:14:35.460 --> 00:14:39.120 align:middle line:84%
Could scientists finally be
tapping into the mathematics

00:14:39.120 --> 00:14:41.550 align:middle line:84%
that reveals the
secrets of the Old One,

00:14:41.550 --> 00:14:43.470 align:middle line:90%
as Einstein would have put it?

00:14:43.470 --> 00:14:45.400 align:middle line:90%
That remains to be seen.

00:14:45.400 --> 00:14:47.180 align:middle line:84%
I believe they're
getting closer,

00:14:47.180 --> 00:14:51.060 align:middle line:84%
but they are still
missing key components.

00:14:51.060 --> 00:14:53.460 align:middle line:84%
Before we get into that,
there is one final thing

00:14:53.460 --> 00:14:56.040 align:middle line:84%
on the amplituhedron
idea to explore.

00:14:56.040 --> 00:14:57.960 align:middle line:84%
The physicists
working on this model

00:14:57.960 --> 00:15:00.740 align:middle line:84%
believe that they have
discovered a master

00:15:00.740 --> 00:15:01.999 align:middle line:90%
amplituhedron.

00:15:01.999 --> 00:15:03.040 align:middle line:90%
Well what does that mean?

00:15:03.040 --> 00:15:04.620 align:middle line:90%
How is it any different?

00:15:04.620 --> 00:15:06.330 align:middle line:84%
It was mentioned
before that there

00:15:06.330 --> 00:15:08.430 align:middle line:84%
are many of these
geometric objects

00:15:08.430 --> 00:15:12.030 align:middle line:84%
because there are many ways
in which particles interact.

00:15:12.030 --> 00:15:16.830 align:middle line:84%
Physicists now believe that
all those specific amplituhedra

00:15:16.830 --> 00:15:20.730 align:middle line:84%
are simply facets on the surface
of a more all encompassing

00:15:20.730 --> 00:15:22.770 align:middle line:90%
master structure.

00:15:22.770 --> 00:15:26.430 align:middle line:84%
This master structure would have
an infinite number of facets,

00:15:26.430 --> 00:15:30.630 align:middle line:84%
kind of like how a circle has
an infinite number of sides,

00:15:30.630 --> 00:15:34.200 align:middle line:84%
only this structure is much
more multi-dimensional.

00:15:34.200 --> 00:15:37.040 align:middle line:84%
The volume of this
master structure

00:15:37.040 --> 00:15:41.230 align:middle line:84%
would then theoretically give us
the total probability amplitude

00:15:41.230 --> 00:15:45.910 align:middle line:84%
of all physical processes
allowed in the universe.

00:15:45.910 --> 00:15:49.270 align:middle line:84%
It would be like their
Philosopher's Stone.

00:15:49.270 --> 00:15:52.210 align:middle line:84%
It could explain why our
physical universe appears

00:15:52.210 --> 00:15:56.830 align:middle line:84%
to exist, why we only experience
three dimensions of space,

00:15:56.830 --> 00:15:59.700 align:middle line:84%
why time appears to
only move forward,

00:15:59.700 --> 00:16:02.600 align:middle line:84%
and why spacetime
appears at all,

00:16:02.600 --> 00:16:05.560 align:middle line:84%
and how the Big Bang
and cosmology arose out

00:16:05.560 --> 00:16:07.810 align:middle line:90%
of pure geometry.

00:16:07.810 --> 00:16:11.800 align:middle line:84%
If this model or another one
similar to it proves correct,

00:16:11.800 --> 00:16:14.920 align:middle line:84%
then it will confirm that
spacetime is illusory,

00:16:14.920 --> 00:16:18.850 align:middle line:84%
and it will lead to a
profound shift in paradigm.

00:16:18.850 --> 00:16:21.850 align:middle line:84%
This master geometric
structure would

00:16:21.850 --> 00:16:26.410 align:middle line:84%
be of infinite dimensionality,
but that dimensionality is not

00:16:26.410 --> 00:16:28.120 align:middle line:90%
in spacetime.

00:16:28.120 --> 00:16:32.560 align:middle line:84%
Rather, it is in an abstract
realm of pure numbers.

00:16:32.560 --> 00:16:36.400 align:middle line:84%
While all phenomenon, such as
spacetime, separate forces,

00:16:36.400 --> 00:16:39.250 align:middle line:84%
particle interactions, and
even our earthly lives,

00:16:39.250 --> 00:16:42.670 align:middle line:84%
are simply emergent properties
from a deeper infinite

00:16:42.670 --> 00:16:44.180 align:middle line:90%
wholeness.

00:16:44.180 --> 00:16:47.140 align:middle line:84%
The changes we experience
in this physical realm

00:16:47.140 --> 00:16:51.250 align:middle line:84%
arise from the structure, the
different facets of that master

00:16:51.250 --> 00:16:54.220 align:middle line:84%
geometry, as it
moves and rotates

00:16:54.220 --> 00:16:57.490 align:middle line:84%
in the quantum sea
of the multiverse.

00:16:57.490 --> 00:17:01.480 align:middle line:84%
But the object itself is
changeless and timeless.

00:17:01.480 --> 00:17:04.359 align:middle line:84%
I just love this because
it relates to the mystery

00:17:04.359 --> 00:17:07.270 align:middle line:84%
teachings on how the
spiritual realms interact

00:17:07.270 --> 00:17:09.250 align:middle line:90%
with our physical realm.

00:17:09.250 --> 00:17:11.410 align:middle line:84%
Before we get into that,
there is one caveat

00:17:11.410 --> 00:17:14.890 align:middle line:84%
to say in regards to this
amplituhedron model, which

00:17:14.890 --> 00:17:19.569 align:middle line:84%
is that so far it is based
on a simplified supersymmetry

00:17:19.569 --> 00:17:22.760 align:middle line:84%
