Let's now explore some mystery
teachings on this topic.

00:17:40.420 --> 00:17:43.120 align:middle line:84%
Nikola Tesla, the great
inventor who is an initiate,

00:17:43.120 --> 00:17:46.120 align:middle line:84%
said, "if you want to find
the secrets of the universe,

00:17:46.120 --> 00:17:49.990 align:middle line:84%
think in terms of energy,
frequency, and vibration."

00:17:49.990 --> 00:17:52.630 align:middle line:84%
He lived his life
applying things

00:17:52.630 --> 00:17:56.560 align:middle line:84%
like numerology and sacred
geometry to all he did,

00:17:56.560 --> 00:18:00.190 align:middle line:84%
such as repeating
everything in sets of three.

00:18:00.190 --> 00:18:04.000 align:middle line:10%
He said, "if you only knew
the magnificence of the 3, 6,

00:18:04.000 --> 00:18:07.690 align:middle line:10%
and 9, then you would have
the keys to the universe."

00:18:07.690 --> 00:18:10.420 align:middle line:84%
Why did Tesla make
claims like these?

00:18:10.420 --> 00:18:13.810 align:middle line:84%
What's so special about
frequency, vibration, numbers,

00:18:13.810 --> 00:18:15.490 align:middle line:90%
and sacred geometry?

00:18:15.490 --> 00:18:18.430 align:middle line:84%
Kabbalah works deeply
with these things

00:18:18.430 --> 00:18:22.510 align:middle line:84%
as the fundamental building
blocks of all creation.

00:18:22.510 --> 00:18:26.140 align:middle line:84%
The Sepher Yetzirah, the
Kabbalistic Book of Formation,

00:18:26.140 --> 00:18:28.600 align:middle line:84%
opens with a secret
wisdom teaching

00:18:28.600 --> 00:18:31.990 align:middle line:84%
that says God, or a
divine creative source,

00:18:31.990 --> 00:18:36.650 align:middle line:84%
engraved his name by three
seraphim, numbers, letters,

00:18:36.650 --> 00:18:38.020 align:middle line:90%
and sounds.

00:18:38.020 --> 00:18:40.200 align:middle line:84%
And the word seraphim
means mighty angel.

00:18:40.200 --> 00:18:44.000 align:middle line:84%
So right away we're being
taught that numbers, letters,

00:18:44.000 --> 00:18:48.700 align:middle line:84%
and sounds are angelic
or spiritual forces.

00:18:48.700 --> 00:18:51.550 align:middle line:10%
It then goes on to
describe these further.

00:18:51.550 --> 00:18:55.120 align:middle line:10%
It says 10 are the
ineffable sefirot,

00:18:55.120 --> 00:18:59.200 align:middle line:10%
meaning the essence of
the numbers 1 through 10.

00:18:59.200 --> 00:19:01.600 align:middle line:10%
Then 22 are the
letters, which it calls

00:19:01.600 --> 00:19:04.250 align:middle line:10%
the foundation of all things.

00:19:04.250 --> 00:19:07.210 align:middle line:10%
And these are grouped into
three mothers, seven doubles,

00:19:07.210 --> 00:19:08.870 align:middle line:10%
and 12 simple letters.

00:19:08.870 --> 00:19:12.580 align:middle line:10%
All together, these 10
sefirot and 22 letters

00:19:12.580 --> 00:19:17.570 align:middle line:10%
form what are called the 32
wonderful paths of wisdom.

00:19:17.570 --> 00:19:19.540 align:middle line:84%
Now what are the
Kabbalists telling us?

00:19:19.540 --> 00:19:22.360 align:middle line:84%
Right away, they are saying
how important numbers

00:19:22.360 --> 00:19:26.080 align:middle line:84%
are as fundamental building
blocks of creation.

00:19:26.080 --> 00:19:29.810 align:middle line:84%
The divine uses
numbers to create.

00:19:29.810 --> 00:19:30.790 align:middle line:90%
But hold on.

00:19:30.790 --> 00:19:33.160 align:middle line:90%
What is meant by numbers?

00:19:33.160 --> 00:19:35.380 align:middle line:84%
The sefirot out are
not ordinary numbers

00:19:35.380 --> 00:19:37.540 align:middle line:90%
in the dry mathematical sense.

00:19:37.540 --> 00:19:41.590 align:middle line:84%
Rather, each number represents
a frequency, or, we could say,

00:19:41.590 --> 00:19:43.790 align:middle line:90%
a ray of creation.

00:19:43.790 --> 00:19:47.590 align:middle line:84%
These numbers are alive,
conscious, purpose-driven

00:19:47.590 --> 00:19:50.020 align:middle line:84%
spiritual light,
or rays of creation

00:19:50.020 --> 00:19:52.240 align:middle line:90%
that emanate from the source.

00:19:52.240 --> 00:19:56.300 align:middle line:10%
Each number contains volumes
worth of information within it,

00:19:56.300 --> 00:19:59.560 align:middle line:10%
and each one represents
an essential aspect

00:19:59.560 --> 00:20:02.140 align:middle line:10%
of divine source.

00:20:02.140 --> 00:20:05.140 align:middle line:10%
The 10 sefirot,
the first 10 rays,

00:20:05.140 --> 00:20:08.080 align:middle line:10%
are arranged in the
pattern of the tree of life

00:20:08.080 --> 00:20:11.050 align:middle line:10%
in the order of the
lightning flash.

00:20:11.050 --> 00:20:14.540 align:middle line:10%
But the divine building
blocks are not only numbers.

00:20:14.540 --> 00:20:16.060 align:middle line:10%
It's also letters.

00:20:16.060 --> 00:20:18.010 align:middle line:90%
What is meant by letters here?

00:20:18.010 --> 00:20:21.370 align:middle line:84%
Well, in Kabbalah, every letter
has a corresponding number

00:20:21.370 --> 00:20:23.470 align:middle line:90%
as its foundational essence.

00:20:23.470 --> 00:20:25.810 align:middle line:84%
But the letters then
take things further.

00:20:25.810 --> 00:20:27.910 align:middle line:90%
The letters form patterns.

00:20:27.910 --> 00:20:31.780 align:middle line:84%
A number is like a pure
singular frequency,

00:20:31.780 --> 00:20:34.690 align:middle line:84%
while a letter is a
pattern shaped out

00:20:34.690 --> 00:20:37.300 align:middle line:90%
of a combination of frequencies.

00:20:37.300 --> 00:20:40.900 align:middle line:84%
Perhaps it's like how when two
waves of different frequencies

00:20:40.900 --> 00:20:43.990 align:middle line:84%
combine they form an
interference pattern that

00:20:43.990 --> 00:20:45.940 align:middle line:90%
shapes a letter.

00:20:45.940 --> 00:20:50.470 align:middle line:84%
So a letter is in essence a
pure geometric arrangement

00:20:50.470 --> 00:20:51.420 align:middle line:90%
of energy.

00:20:51.420 --> 00:20:53.680 align:middle line:84%
Is this starting
to sound familiar?

00:20:53.680 --> 00:20:58.360 align:middle line:84%
Could we compare each letter
to a specific amplituhedron?

00:20:58.360 --> 00:21:01.210 align:middle line:84%
If we were to use this
analogy, let's then

00:21:01.210 --> 00:21:02.930 align:middle line:90%
take it a bit further.

00:21:02.930 --> 00:21:06.610 align:middle line:84%
Remember how the physicists talk
about a master amplituhedron

00:21:06.610 --> 00:21:10.300 align:middle line:84%
as being somewhat equivalent
to a circle, where all lesser

00:21:10.300 --> 00:21:15.270 align:middle line:84%
amplituhedra sit on the surface
facets of that master geometry?

00:21:15.270 --> 00:21:17.770 align:middle line:10%
Well, in a similar way,
the Sepher Yetzirah

00:21:17.770 --> 00:21:21.100 align:middle line:10%
talks about how all 22
letters are arranged

00:21:21.100 --> 00:21:23.380 align:middle line:10%
as if upon a sphere.

00:21:23.380 --> 00:21:26.140 align:middle line:10%
Each letter is then
combined or connected

00:21:26.140 --> 00:21:30.400 align:middle line:10%
with all the other letters,
forming pairs of letters.

00:21:30.400 --> 00:21:34.990 align:middle line:10%
This produces what is called
the 231 gates of knowledge,

00:21:34.990 --> 00:21:37.730 align:middle line:10%
or we could say information.

00:21:37.730 --> 00:21:40.000 align:middle line:84%
Although knowledge is really
a better word because it

00:21:40.000 --> 00:21:42.550 align:middle line:90%
implies intelligence.

00:21:42.550 --> 00:21:48.160 align:middle line:84%
This master structure of the
231 gates can then be rotated.

00:21:48.160 --> 00:21:51.190 align:middle line:84%
When it is rotated
forward or clockwise

00:21:51.190 --> 00:21:53.840 align:middle line:84%
it leads to good and
pleasurable things.

00:21:53.840 --> 00:21:57.070 align:middle line:84%
But when it is rotated
backwards or counterclockwise

00:21:57.070 --> 00:21:59.830 align:middle line:84%
we are told that it leads
to evil and torment.

00:21:59.830 --> 00:22:02.830 align:middle line:84%
This reveals to us that
forward or clockwise

00:22:02.830 --> 00:22:05.680 align:middle line:84%
is aligned with the
will to do good,

00:22:05.680 --> 00:22:07.960 align:middle line:84%
while backward or
counterclockwise is

00:22:07.960 --> 00:22:09.970 align:middle line:90%
against that will.

00:22:09.970 --> 00:22:13.000 align:middle line:84%
One simple way to apply
this is to train ourselves

00:22:13.000 --> 00:22:17.470 align:middle line:84%
to draw or write our
zeros and Os clockwise

00:22:17.470 --> 00:22:21.340 align:middle line:84%
with the intent of aligning with
the forward flow or the will

00:22:21.340 --> 00:22:22.240 align:middle line:90%
to do good.

00:22:22.240 --> 00:22:26.110 align:middle line:84%
Try it out, and pay attention
to how you draw circles.

