Another important
key to the letters

00:22:28.210 --> 00:22:32.180 align:middle line:84%
is that they all represent
a transformational process.

00:22:32.180 --> 00:22:35.500 align:middle line:10%
When we look at the tree
of life each path or letter

00:22:35.500 --> 00:22:37.350 align:middle line:10%
connects two spheres.

00:22:37.350 --> 00:22:41.590 align:middle line:10%
The spheres, or the numbers, are
considered as states of being,

00:22:41.590 --> 00:22:43.360 align:middle line:10%
while the paths,
or the letters, are

00:22:43.360 --> 00:22:45.340 align:middle line:10%
more like states of becoming.

00:22:45.340 --> 00:22:49.130 align:middle line:84%
They are a transformation from
one state of being to another.

00:22:49.130 --> 00:22:53.890 align:middle line:84%
So the letters could be akin
to the dynamics of interaction

00:22:53.890 --> 00:22:57.340 align:middle line:84%
between particles, which are
more like states of being.

00:22:57.340 --> 00:22:59.920 align:middle line:84%
This would match up
again with the idea

00:22:59.920 --> 00:23:04.390 align:middle line:84%
of the amplituhedron, which is
based on particle interactions.

00:23:04.390 --> 00:23:08.230 align:middle line:84%
There is a reason why so many
ancient mystery traditions put

00:23:08.230 --> 00:23:12.130 align:middle line:84%
a lot of emphasis on
learning to read and write

00:23:12.130 --> 00:23:15.190 align:middle line:84%
ancient languages and
magical alphabets.

00:23:15.190 --> 00:23:18.340 align:middle line:84%
Good examples of this are
ancient Hebrew, Sanskrit,

00:23:18.340 --> 00:23:20.740 align:middle line:84%
and Japanese kanji,
all of which are

00:23:20.740 --> 00:23:23.920 align:middle line:84%
said to be among the few
remaining ancient languages we

00:23:23.920 --> 00:23:27.130 align:middle line:84%
still really understand
that were derived from what

00:23:27.130 --> 00:23:30.280 align:middle line:84%
are called the fire letters,
or the original language

00:23:30.280 --> 00:23:31.930 align:middle line:90%
of creation.

00:23:31.930 --> 00:23:35.140 align:middle line:10%
As we can also see
by now, the formation

00:23:35.140 --> 00:23:38.470 align:middle line:10%
of both the tree of
life and the 231 gates,

00:23:38.470 --> 00:23:40.540 align:middle line:10%
which are based
upon the letters,

00:23:40.540 --> 00:23:43.030 align:middle line:10%
give us a variety of
sacred geometries.

00:23:43.030 --> 00:23:48.070 align:middle line:10%
As the pure frequencies of the
numbers combine or intersect,

00:23:48.070 --> 00:23:49.390 align:middle line:10%
it gives the letters.

00:23:49.390 --> 00:23:52.570 align:middle line:10%
And then, as these combine
again in various ways,

00:23:52.570 --> 00:23:55.180 align:middle line:10%
it results in sacred geometries.

00:23:55.180 --> 00:24:00.400 align:middle line:10%
Within these master patterns we
can find all sacred geometries.

00:24:00.400 --> 00:24:02.590 align:middle line:10%
Just start connecting
the dots and we'll

00:24:02.590 --> 00:24:04.480 align:middle line:10%
find all the
fundamental patterns

00:24:04.480 --> 00:24:07.970 align:middle line:10%
our universe is built on.

00:24:07.970 --> 00:24:11.430 align:middle line:84%
And so the Sepher Yetzirah
says that from nothingness

00:24:11.430 --> 00:24:14.220 align:middle line:84%
the source Ein Sof
made something.

00:24:14.220 --> 00:24:16.230 align:middle line:90%
From nothing comes something.

00:24:16.230 --> 00:24:20.850 align:middle line:84%
From the empty void is
made the material world,

00:24:20.850 --> 00:24:24.210 align:middle line:84%
using these numbers,
letters, and sounds.

00:24:24.210 --> 00:24:25.890 align:middle line:90%
Let's explore sounds now.

00:24:25.890 --> 00:24:27.510 align:middle line:90%
How do they fit in?

00:24:27.510 --> 00:24:29.880 align:middle line:90%
Well, sounds are vibration.

00:24:29.880 --> 00:24:32.460 align:middle line:84%
The inner essence
of a letter is based

00:24:32.460 --> 00:24:34.440 align:middle line:90%
on numbers or frequencies.

00:24:34.440 --> 00:24:36.600 align:middle line:84%
But the outer
expression of letters

00:24:36.600 --> 00:24:40.170 align:middle line:90%
produces sound or vibrations.

00:24:40.170 --> 00:24:44.700 align:middle line:84%
We know from the research of
Swiss scientist Dr. Hans Jenny

00:24:44.700 --> 00:24:47.520 align:middle line:84%
and many others who followed
in his footsteps, when

00:24:47.520 --> 00:24:50.490 align:middle line:84%
the right sounds are
exposed to certain materia,

00:24:50.490 --> 00:24:54.570 align:middle line:84%
such as water, clay, or
sand, it shapes that materia

00:24:54.570 --> 00:24:56.910 align:middle line:90%
into sacred geometric patterns.

00:24:56.910 --> 00:24:59.400 align:middle line:84%
He called this research
cymatics, or the study

00:24:59.400 --> 00:25:01.660 align:middle line:90%
of wave phenomenon.

00:25:01.660 --> 00:25:03.990 align:middle line:84%
But what is meant
by the right sounds?

00:25:03.990 --> 00:25:06.060 align:middle line:84%
Well, it means a
sound or vibration

00:25:06.060 --> 00:25:09.780 align:middle line:84%
that is resonant with
that particular materia.

00:25:09.780 --> 00:25:12.480 align:middle line:84%
Vibrational resonance
is one of the principles

00:25:12.480 --> 00:25:15.840 align:middle line:84%
that Nikola Tesla used in
his various inventions.

00:25:15.840 --> 00:25:20.070 align:middle line:84%
Resonance implies the
laws of harmony and music.

00:25:20.070 --> 00:25:23.190 align:middle line:10%
These laws have to
do with ratios or how

00:25:23.190 --> 00:25:26.130 align:middle line:10%
one frequency relates
to another, whether they

00:25:26.130 --> 00:25:28.470 align:middle line:10%
harmonize or not.

00:25:28.470 --> 00:25:31.380 align:middle line:10%
For example, in the standard
musical scale of an octave,

00:25:31.380 --> 00:25:32.400 align:middle line:10%
there are eighth notes.

00:25:32.400 --> 00:25:35.730 align:middle line:10%
Do, re, mi, fa,
so, la, ti, and do.

00:25:35.730 --> 00:25:39.030 align:middle line:10%
That next do, the eighth note,
is actually the first note

00:25:39.030 --> 00:25:41.080 align:middle line:10%
on the next octave higher.

00:25:41.080 --> 00:25:46.200 align:middle line:10%
So the second do is a higher
harmonic of the first.

00:25:46.200 --> 00:25:49.500 align:middle line:84%
This is a one to eight
ratio, the first note

00:25:49.500 --> 00:25:51.570 align:middle line:84%
and the eighth
note in an octave.

00:25:51.570 --> 00:25:53.370 align:middle line:84%
Although, in terms
of frequency, it is

00:25:53.370 --> 00:25:55.890 align:middle line:90%
double the rate of vibration.

00:25:55.890 --> 00:25:57.540 align:middle line:84%
The other way we
can get harmony,

00:25:57.540 --> 00:26:00.450 align:middle line:84%
besides going up an
octave, is to use

00:26:00.450 --> 00:26:03.720 align:middle line:84%
what is called the
perfect fifth in music.

00:26:03.720 --> 00:26:06.600 align:middle line:84%
That is to take the
fifth note, the so chord,

00:26:06.600 --> 00:26:08.820 align:middle line:90%
and combine it with the eighth.

00:26:08.820 --> 00:26:11.340 align:middle line:10%
This is a five to
eight ratio, which

00:26:11.340 --> 00:26:14.700 align:middle line:10%
is what we call a golden ratio.

00:26:14.700 --> 00:26:16.470 align:middle line:10%
What is a golden ratio?

00:26:16.470 --> 00:26:18.930 align:middle line:10%
It relates to the
Fibonacci sequence.

00:26:18.930 --> 00:26:22.320 align:middle line:10%
Starting with the basic
binary of 0 and 1,

00:26:22.320 --> 00:26:24.690 align:middle line:10%
and then all other
numbers in this sequence

00:26:24.690 --> 00:26:28.650 align:middle line:10%
derive from adding the two
numbers that preceded it.

00:26:28.650 --> 00:26:31.380 align:middle line:10%
But what's most interesting
about this sequence is

00:26:31.380 --> 00:26:35.400 align:middle line:10%
that when we take the ratio
of any two sequential numbers

00:26:35.400 --> 00:26:39.120 align:middle line:10%
it begins to converge to what
is known as the phi ratio,

00:26:39.120 --> 00:26:43.680 align:middle line:10%
or golden ratio, of
1.618 dot, dot, dot.

00:26:43.680 --> 00:26:49.590 align:middle line:10%
Notice that the 5 to 8 ratio
is in this Fibonacci sequence.

00:26:49.590 --> 00:26:53.550 align:middle line:10%
This golden ratio shows up
all over nature in the cosmos,

00:26:53.550 --> 00:26:56.430 align:middle line:10%
from the way that plants
grow to the proportions

00:26:56.430 --> 00:26:59.400 align:middle line:10%
of our own bodies to
the golden spirals

00:26:59.400 --> 00:27:04.650 align:middle line:10%
we see in shells, flowers, pine
cones, ferns, even all the way

00:27:04.650 --> 00:27:07.140 align:middle line:10%
up to spiral galaxies.

00:27:07.140 --> 00:27:10.320 align:middle line:84%
The beauty of it is that
the same ratios that

00:27:10.320 --> 00:27:13.140 align:middle line:84%
govern the laws of
harmony and music

00:27:13.140 --> 00:27:16.860 align:middle line:84%
also govern the laws
of sacred geometry.

00:27:16.860 --> 00:27:18.900 align:middle line:84%
Returning to cymatics
for a moment,

00:27:18.900 --> 00:27:22.170 align:middle line:84%
Hans Jenny mostly studied the
effects of pure frequencies

00:27:22.170 --> 00:27:23.772 align:middle line:90%
on various materia.

00:27:23.772 --> 00:27:25.230 align:middle line:84%
But there were a
few studies he did

00:27:25.230 --> 00:27:28.230 align:middle line:84%
that combined different
frequencies, such as

00:27:28.230 --> 00:27:30.960 align:middle line:84%
might be associated with the
sounds of different letter

00:27:30.960 --> 00:27:33.300 align:middle line:90%
combinations from Kabbalah.

00:27:33.300 --> 00:27:36.140 align:middle line:90%
Letters combine to form words.

00:27:36.140 --> 00:27:40.140 align:middle line:84%
In many spiritual traditions,
certain divine names or words

00:27:40.140 --> 00:27:43.890 align:middle line:84%
of power are used as
mantras and chants.

00:27:43.890 --> 00:27:47.640 align:middle line:10%
For example, Kabbalah talks
about the various names of God,

00:27:47.640 --> 00:27:50.940 align:middle line:10%
such as the yud-hey-vav-hey
or the Tetragrammaton,

00:27:50.940 --> 00:27:55.490 align:middle line:10%
as being more like
formulas for creation.

00:27:55.490 --> 00:28:00.030 align:middle line:84%
While in Sanskrit, ohm is said
to be the primordial sound

00:28:00.030 --> 00:28:01.530 align:middle line:90%
of creation.

00:28:01.530 --> 00:28:05.040 align:middle line:10%
Some have even claimed
that when ohm is properly

00:28:05.040 --> 00:28:07.380 align:middle line:10%
intoned across a
plate of sand it

00:28:07.380 --> 00:28:11.220 align:middle line:10%
will shape the sand into
what looks like a Sri Yantra.

00:28:11.220 --> 00:28:12.990 align:middle line:90%
It's possible.

00:28:12.990 --> 00:28:15.900 align:middle line:84%
But without a doubt,
the vibrational energy

00:28:15.900 --> 00:28:19.530 align:middle line:84%
of sound moves and
organizes matter.

00:28:19.530 --> 00:28:23.760 align:middle line:84%
We can imagine that if either
spacetime or the quantum sea

00:28:23.760 --> 00:28:28.200 align:middle line:84%
is a superfluid, then
vibration of divine names

00:28:28.200 --> 00:28:31.650 align:middle line:84%
or words of power
shape that superfluid

00:28:31.650 --> 00:28:35.760 align:middle line:84%
into sacred geometric patterns,
like we see in cymatics.

00:28:35.760 --> 00:28:39.050 align:middle line:90%


00:28:39.050 --> 00:28:42.470 align:middle line:84%
This is one way that the
higher rays of creation,

00:28:42.470 --> 00:28:45.650 align:middle line:84%
such as numbers and letters,
can make the transition

00:28:45.650 --> 00:28:49.250 align:middle line:84%
from the realm of pure spirit
into the realm of physicality.

00:28:49.250 --> 00:28:52.290 align:middle line:90%


00:28:52.290 --> 00:28:55.800 align:middle line:84%
The final missing key in physics
models that we've discussed

00:28:55.800 --> 00:28:58.340 align:middle line:84%
is consciousness,
the spirit which

00:28:58.340 --> 00:29:01.230 align:middle line:90%
resides in non-physical realms.

00:29:01.230 --> 00:29:03.390 align:middle line:84%
The hermetic
principle of mentalism

00:29:03.390 --> 00:29:08.160 align:middle line:84%
that consciousness, or mind,
is primary must be included.

00:29:08.160 --> 00:29:10.950 align:middle line:84%
So long as scientists
remain rigidly opposed

00:29:10.950 --> 00:29:14.220 align:middle line:84%
to bringing consciousness into
their grand unified theories,

00:29:14.220 --> 00:29:18.330 align:middle line:84%
they will fail to find a
true theory of everything.

00:29:18.330 --> 00:29:21.210 align:middle line:84%
As Tesla said, "the
day science begins

00:29:21.210 --> 00:29:23.820 align:middle line:84%
to study non-physical
phenomena, it

00:29:23.820 --> 00:29:26.370 align:middle line:84%
will make more
progress in one decade

00:29:26.370 --> 00:29:29.790 align:middle line:84%
than in all the previous
centuries of existence."

00:29:29.790 --> 00:29:33.000 align:middle line:84%
The newer physics models
based on geometry and laws

00:29:33.000 --> 00:29:35.550 align:middle line:84%
of vibrational harmony
start to approach

00:29:35.550 --> 00:29:39.360 align:middle line:84%
this, especially when these
are combined with Kabbalistic

00:29:39.360 --> 00:29:41.730 align:middle line:90%
and other metaphysical wisdoms.

00:29:41.730 --> 00:29:45.930 align:middle line:84%
But how does all of this
apply to us and our lives?

00:29:45.930 --> 00:29:47.700 align:middle line:84%
With these
understandings, we become

00:29:47.700 --> 00:29:50.310 align:middle line:84%
empowered to use
our consciousness

00:29:50.310 --> 00:29:53.910 align:middle line:84%
to properly communicate
with deeper reality.

00:29:53.910 --> 00:29:57.660 align:middle line:84%
By doing so, we can
impact how it manifests

00:29:57.660 --> 00:29:59.790 align:middle line:90%
in our experiential realm.

00:29:59.790 --> 00:30:04.020 align:middle line:10%
We and everything around us
are made of numbers, letters,

00:30:04.020 --> 00:30:06.600 align:middle line:10%
sounds, and sacred geometries.

00:30:06.600 --> 00:30:10.230 align:middle line:84%
As we learn the true
underlying meaning and essence

00:30:10.230 --> 00:30:13.920 align:middle line:84%
of each of these building
blocks, as well as properly

00:30:13.920 --> 00:30:18.210 align:middle line:84%
tune our instruments, which
is our body, mind, and soul,

00:30:18.210 --> 00:30:21.910 align:middle line:84%
we can then use
these tools, as well.

00:30:21.910 --> 00:30:24.060 align:middle line:84%
This is something
Kabbalah and other mystery

00:30:24.060 --> 00:30:28.110 align:middle line:84%
teachings have developed deep
arts and sciences around.

00:30:28.110 --> 00:30:31.230 align:middle line:84%
We can learn to apply
them in magical ways

00:30:31.230 --> 00:30:35.070 align:middle line:84%
to enter into a co-creative
relationship with the universe

00:30:35.070 --> 00:30:36.570 align:middle line:90%
and source.

00:30:36.570 --> 00:30:38.250 align:middle line:84%
One of the big
keys to doing this

00:30:38.250 --> 00:30:41.670 align:middle line:84%
correctly is by properly
tuning ourselves

00:30:41.670 --> 00:30:45.060 align:middle line:84%
to the higher energies
of spirit consciousness.

00:30:45.060 --> 00:30:47.910 align:middle line:10%
Kabbalah talks about
ascending and descending

00:30:47.910 --> 00:30:49.140 align:middle line:10%
the tree of life.

00:30:49.140 --> 00:30:52.560 align:middle line:10%
From the physical world of
diversity that we are in,

00:30:52.560 --> 00:30:57.240 align:middle line:10%
we strive to ascend back
to the unity with source.

00:30:57.240 --> 00:31:00.750 align:middle line:10%
Simultaneously, spirit
seeks to express itself

00:31:00.750 --> 00:31:03.990 align:middle line:10%
into the world of matter
by descending the tree.

00:31:03.990 --> 00:31:08.490 align:middle line:84%
Kabbalah also teaches that the
best way to align with source

00:31:08.490 --> 00:31:11.010 align:middle line:84%
and feel that
connection in our lives

00:31:11.010 --> 00:31:13.445 align:middle line:90%
is to live in the middle pillar.

00:31:13.445 --> 00:31:15.690 align:middle line:90%
Well, what does that mean?

00:31:15.690 --> 00:31:18.600 align:middle line:84%
At the top of the
middle pillar is unity.

00:31:18.600 --> 00:31:24.030 align:middle line:84%
For us, this means being aware
that we are one with all.

00:31:24.030 --> 00:31:26.280 align:middle line:84%
The next step down
the middle pillar

00:31:26.280 --> 00:31:28.620 align:middle line:84%
is about hidden
knowledge and revealing

00:31:28.620 --> 00:31:32.280 align:middle line:84%
the connection between the
physical and spiritual realms.

00:31:32.280 --> 00:31:36.780 align:middle line:84%
The center is about expressing
and recognizing beauty

00:31:36.780 --> 00:31:39.630 align:middle line:90%
in all things great and small.

00:31:39.630 --> 00:31:41.760 align:middle line:10%
Then we come to the
foundation, which

00:31:41.760 --> 00:31:45.740 align:middle line:10%
is about grasping how the
laws of the universe work.

00:31:45.740 --> 00:31:49.710 align:middle line:10%
And at the very practical level,
patterning our daily lives

00:31:49.710 --> 00:31:52.980 align:middle line:10%
through what we
think, say, and do

00:31:52.980 --> 00:31:55.950 align:middle line:10%
to be aligned and in
the flow with those laws

00:31:55.950 --> 00:31:57.090 align:middle line:10%
of the universe.

00:31:57.090 --> 00:31:59.190 align:middle line:84%
Finally, at the bottom
of the middle pillar

00:31:59.190 --> 00:32:02.160 align:middle line:84%
is the physical kingdom
in which we live, move,

00:32:02.160 --> 00:32:05.280 align:middle line:84%
and have our experience
of being embodied.

00:32:05.280 --> 00:32:09.180 align:middle line:84%
We are here so that
we can learn the art

00:32:09.180 --> 00:32:13.650 align:middle line:84%
and science of manifesting our
full potential into this world.

00:32:13.650 --> 00:32:18.640 align:middle line:84%
We are eternal spirit beings
having a physical experience,

00:32:18.640 --> 00:32:20.790 align:middle line:90%
not the other way around.

00:32:20.790 --> 00:32:23.610 align:middle line:84%
When we can truly
grasp this wisdom,

00:32:23.610 --> 00:32:27.300 align:middle line:84%
that is when our entire paradigm
of how we live in this world

00:32:27.300 --> 00:32:30.390 align:middle line:84%
will completely shift,
making life so much more

00:32:30.390 --> 00:32:33.660 align:middle line:90%
fun and full of true joy.

00:32:33.660 --> 00:32:35.520 align:middle line:90%
Why is all this important?

00:32:35.520 --> 00:32:40.050 align:middle line:84%
The search for unity,
knowledge, beauty, foundation,

00:32:40.050 --> 00:32:43.110 align:middle line:84%
and understanding life
in the physical world

00:32:43.110 --> 00:32:48.240 align:middle line:84%
is the search of both physicists
and metaphysicists alike.

00:32:48.240 --> 00:32:51.390 align:middle line:84%
It helps us to make sense
of this grand experience

00:32:51.390 --> 00:32:53.970 align:middle line:90%
that we are all a part of.

00:32:53.970 --> 00:32:57.450 align:middle line:84%
It can bring us meaning
and clarity of purpose.

00:32:57.450 --> 00:32:59.910 align:middle line:84%
It can also help us
to learn to harness

00:32:59.910 --> 00:33:03.570 align:middle line:84%
the potentials available
to us and hopefully

00:33:03.570 --> 00:33:08.760 align:middle line:84%
use them to transform our lives
and our world into better ones.

00:33:08.760 --> 00:33:12.060 align:middle line:84%
As we do, our
transformation sends ripples

00:33:12.060 --> 00:33:16.500 align:middle line:84%
throughout the cosmos
because we are the cosmos.

00:33:16.500 --> 00:33:20.400 align:middle line:84%
We are entangled with every
part of this universe.

00:33:20.400 --> 00:33:24.660 align:middle line:84%
So, yes, our efforts
for growth and expansion

00:33:24.660 --> 00:33:29.700 align:middle line:84%
do matter in ways far beyond
what most of us realize.

00:33:29.700 --> 00:33:33.570 align:middle line:84%
When we learn to become
players in the cosmic orchestra

00:33:33.570 --> 00:33:35.580 align:middle line:84%
and pluck the
strings of creation

00:33:35.580 --> 00:33:38.190 align:middle line:84%
to make beautiful
music, that is when

00:33:38.190 --> 00:33:41.640 align:middle line:84%
we will earn our rightful place
in this grand play of life.

